parameters:
Tailor Neuro: I'm not excited enough... If lightning doesn't
strike, I can't get any work done...

Tailor Neuro: You've come at a good time! I have prepared a
swimsuit that befits a genius magician!
Tailor Neuro: Now, come over here for the finishing touches!

Magician Relm: I will make sure to thoroughly check if it is
suitable for someone like me!
Thief Nora: Relm-san, you seemed excited!

Priestess Sophia: Even for a genius magician, it's only
natural to have age-appropriate joy.
Clea: Do you two have any interest in swimsuits?

Thief Nora: Oh, well, I mean... I have a big body and all...
so, it wouldn't suit me...

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it would suit you well, Nora-chan.
As for me, well, if there's an opportunity, I suppose.

Magician Relm: Hey, is this... really okay? Isn't it
strange?

Tailor Neuro: It's a perfect finish! I've created a
masterpiece that you won't be embarrassed to wear anywhere!
Magician Relm: If I get laughed at... it'll be your fault!
Magician Relm: H-How does it look...?
Priestess Sophia: Oh my, you look completely different.
Clea: It suits you very well.

Tailor Neuro: When I saw your intelligent and calm
appearance, I had a flash of inspiration! You look just like
the wise sage Atomis from the founding myth!
Magician Relm: I-I'll wear it if everyone says so!
Magician Relm: Ehehe... I did it.

Tailor Neuro: I won't be able to make any new creations for
a while... I've used up everything I gave to you all.

Tailor Neuro: I heard there's a skilled tailor in the Mucos
region. It might be worth looking for them on our journey!

Tailor Neuro: Have you found a tailor in the Mucos region?
For the time being, I'll be working to make a living.
Thief Nora: It's amazing! There are so many clothes!

Cleric Sophia: It seems quite authentic as a tailor shop...
*burp*

Mage Relm: Sophia-san, are you okay? It's not a laughing
matter for a cleric to be in poor health.
Cleric Sophia: I-I'm fine... If I just drink this... *burp*

Tailor Nora: Sorry for the mess! I'm making the payment now,
so please wait!
Clea: Making payment... Is it a good job?

Tailor Nora: It doesn't matter! I got inspired and I'll make
it, that's all!
Tailor Nora: I want to finish it! Sorry, but come over here!

Cleric Sophia: How about going shopping? Even adventurers
need to dress up occasionally.
Thief Nora: Clea-san, you seemed a little happy there.

Mage Relm: Since you seem to come from a good place, have
you had any experience getting clothes tailored?
Cleric Sophia: Oh, are you jealous?

Mage Relm: Well, it's not like I... well, if you ask me, I
guess I can make it for you!
Clea: Um... Are you really going out like this?

Tailor Nora: Of course! It's perfect, I'm glad I made it for
you!
Clea: Understood... I will make up my mind...
Clea: Um... Um... What do you think?

Thief Nora: It suits you very well! It's a cool swimsuit
that suits you, Clea-san!
Cleric Sophia: Hehe, it's really good, isn't it, Relm- chan?
Mage Relm: Hah...! I-I don't think I'm jealous or anything!

Tailor Nora: I had a flash of inspiration when I saw you in
battle, helping others! I thought I should make it based on
King Basileus of the Kingdom of Basileia!

Clea: I can't believe I'm receiving a swimsuit... I'll
treasure it and make good use of it. Thank you very much.

Mage Relm: A-And, I can even make a special swimsuit just
for you!

Tailor Nora: I'm sorry, but I can't do that... I need
inspiration to make it work...

Tailor Nora: Get involved in flashy incidents like this
again! Then I'll definitely make a swimsuit for Miss Clea
too!
Mage Relm: It's a promise, okay!

Tailor Nora: I'm really grateful! If you ever have any
troubles, feel free to consult the guild!
